<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="author" content="Student">
    <meta name="description" content="Example HTML page using basic tags">
    <title>Basic HTML Example</title>
</head>

<body>

<h1>Welcome to My HTML Page</h1>

<p>This page demonstrates the use of <strong>basic HTML tags</strong> and attributes without using any CSS.</p>

<hr>

<h2>About Me</h2>
<p>Hello! My name is John Doe. I enjoy learning web development.</p>

<h3>My Hobbies</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Reading</li>
    <li>Coding</li>
    <li>Playing games</li>
</ul>

<h3>My Goals</h3>
<ol>
    <li>Learn HTML</li>
    <li>Learn CSS</li>
    <li>Learn JavaScript</li>
</ol>

<hr>

<h2>Favorite Website</h2>
<p>Visit 
<a href="https://www.wikipedia.org" target="_blank">Wikipedia</a> 
to learn more about different topics.</p>

<hr>

<h2>Sample Image</h2>
<img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Sample Image" width="150" height="150">

<hr>

<h2>Sample Table</h2>

<table border="1">
    <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Age</th>
        <th>Country</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Ana</td>
        <td>20</td>
        <td>Philippines</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>Mark</td>
        <td>22</td>
        <td>Canada</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<hr>

<h2>Registration Form</h2>

<form action="#" method="post">

<label for="fname">First Name:</label><br>
<input type="text" id="fname" name="fname" required><br><br>

<label for="lname">Last Name:</label><br>
<input type="text" id="lname" name="lname" required><br><br>

<label for="email">Email:</label><br>
<input type="email" id="email" name="email"><br><br>

<label for="password">Password:</label><br>
<input type="password" id="password" name="password"><br><br>

<label for="age">Age:</label><br>
<input type="number" id="age" name="age" min="1" max="120"><br><br>

<label>Gender:</label><br>
<input type="radio" id="male" name="gender" value="male">
<label for="male">Male</label><br>

<input type="radio" id="female" name="gender" value="female">
<label for="female">Female</label><br><br>

<label>Interests:</label><br>
<input type="checkbox" name="interest" value="music"> Music<br>
<input type="checkbox" name="interest" value="sports"> Sports<br>
<input type="checkbox" name="interest" value="coding"> Coding<br><br>

<label for="country">Country:</label><br>
<select id="country" name="country">
    <option value="philippines">Philippines</option>
    <option value="usa">USA</option>
    <option value="japan">Japan</option>
</select><br><br>

<label for="message">Message:</label><br>
<textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" cols="30"></textarea><br><br>

<input type="submit" value="Submit">
<input type="reset" value="Reset">

</form>

<hr>

<footer>
<p>&copy; 2026 My Basic HTML Page</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
